<paragraph id="IFRIC12_15"><paranum>15</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRIC 12"/><data name="paranum" value="15"/></prolog><body><variant base="F32756851" id="IFRIC12_15_V2" principles="no"> <p id="IFRIC12_P0113">If the operator provides construction or upgrade services the consideration received or receivable by the operator shall be recognised in accordance with <xref base="F35362949" href="../ifrs14/IFRS15_TOC.dita#IFRS15_TOC0001" id="IFRIC12_X0114">IFRS 15</xref>. The consideration may be rights to:</p> <ol base="F32756852" id="IFRIC12_L0007" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="F32756854" id="IFRIC12_P0114">a financial asset, or</p> </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="F32756860" id="IFRIC12_P0116">an intangible asset.</p> </li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>